               <p>
                  <hi rend="italic">William Shorter.</hi> I never saw this woman before I was given in charge; I do not know her. <hi rend="italic">Witness.</hi> I have not the least doubt that they are the parties—no one else went into their room to my knowledge—the adjoining room was let.</p>
